Install on Mac OS X

Download Mac installer
Double-click .dmg file
Drag stVi application icon on Application folder
Start stVi application from your Applications folder
(press CTRL to open it the first time it you get a message saying that the tool is not certified)

Install on Ubuntu

Download Ubuntu application package
Extract the archive to a location where you would like to store the program
To start the stVi application open the Terminal at the extracted directory and type ‘./stVi’

Install on Windows

Download Windows client installer
Double click on
Follow the instructions to install stVi on your Windows machine
Search for stVi on your applications folder and launch it
